          <span class="entryTitle">Math Is Easy ...</span>
        </h4>
        <div class="content wiki" lang="x-html"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span/><p><img alt="http://goessner.net/2006/03/findx.jpg" src="http://goessner.net/2006/03/findx.jpg" style="display:block;margin:0 auto;" title="http://goessner.net/2006/03/findx.jpg"/>­
